Program: Discovery
Title: Gene therapy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxm9
Last Broadcast Date: 27 March 2000
Disappointments following the promising development of gene therapy. The treatment has come under the spotlight following the death of a young man with a defect which made him unable to process food. He was healthy when he agreed to the therapy but the genetically altered virus used to replace the faulty gene caused a massive immune response with devastating affects. Show less